code: @Override public void process(Exchange exchange) throws Exception {     String remotePath = DropboxHelper.getRemotePath(configuration, exchange).     DropboxConfigurationValidator.validateDelOp(remotePath).     DropboxDelResult result = new DropboxAPIFacade(configuration.getClient(), exchange).del(remotePath).     exchange.getIn().setHeader(DropboxResultHeader.DELETED_PATH.name(), result.getEntry()).     exchange.getIn().setBody(result.getEntry()).     log.debug("Deleted: {}", remotePath). }
